subject: Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Jimmie Johnson won his second Daytona 500, racing past the defending Nascar champion Brad Keselowski on the final restart, and Danica Patrick finished eighth.
